      <title>伦敦市长誓言在竞选中建造 40,000 套新议会住宅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/london-mayor-vows-40-000-new-council-homes-in-election-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一启动第三次连任竞选的伦敦市长萨迪克·汗 (Sadiq Khan) 承诺，将在本世纪末建造 40,000 套新的议会住宅，作为解决该市住房短缺问题的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/london-mayor-vows-40-000-new-council-homes-in-election-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 13:04:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通的 Dicenso：股市将继续创出新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-18/jpm-s-dicenso-stocks-will-keep-hitting-new-highs-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通私人银行全球投资机会主管莫妮卡·迪森索表示，股市仍可能上涨百分之五、六或七。她在“彭博监控”节目中谈论了如何在这次集会期间让现金发挥作用。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-18/jpm-s-dicenso-stocks-will-keep-hitting-new-highs-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 13:01:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大英百科全书寻求 10 亿美元的 IPO 估值</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/encyclopaedia-britannica-seeking-1-billion-valuation-in-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，大英百科全书公司是一家教育技术公司，也是韦氏词典等书籍的出版商，该公司正在寻求约 10 亿美元的首次公开募股估值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/encyclopaedia-britannica-seeking-1-billion-valuation-in-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 12:58:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊拉克表示将削减石油出口以弥补产量缺口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/iraq-says-will-cut-oil-exports-to-compensate-for-output-breach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊拉克表示，将在未来几个月减少石油出口，以补偿今年早些时候产量超出欧佩克+限制的情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/iraq-says-will-cut-oil-exports-to-compensate-for-output-breach</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 12:51:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>恒大的许先生因夸大业绩而被禁止进入中国市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/china-fines-evergrande-s-hui-and-bans-him-from-market</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国恒大集团前董事长兼创始人许家印被发现存在欺诈行为，中国证券监管机构对其处以 4700 万元人民币（650 万美元）的罚款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/china-fines-evergrande-s-hui-and-bans-him-from-market</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 12:50:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国证券交易委员会因虚假人工智能声明起诉基金经理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/sec-sues-money-managers-for-bogus-artificial-intelligence-claims</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国证券交易委员会对两家基金经理进行了处罚，称其对人工智能的使用存在虚假说法，从而加大了华尔街主要监管机构的打击力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/sec-sues-money-managers-for-bogus-artificial-intelligence-claims</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 12:43:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波音公司的痛苦蔓延至乘客和航空公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-18/boeing-s-pain-spreading-to-passengers-and-airlines-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[波音公司的生产延误开始影响航空公司和乘客。随着波音公司努力解决 737 Max 飞机的安全问题，航空公司目前正在削减夏季航班时刻表。彭博资讯的乔治·弗格森讨论了“彭博监视”对公司和乘客的影响。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-18/boeing-s-pain-spreading-to-passengers-and-airlines-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 12:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴克莱银行着眼于主权财富基金推动投资银行业务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/barclays-eyes-sovereign-wealth-funds-in-investment-banking-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴克莱银行正在寻求扩大与主权财富基金和私募股权巨头的关系，作为其通过扩大咨询和股票承销来提高其投资银行部门盈利能力的努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/barclays-eyes-sovereign-wealth-funds-in-investment-banking-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 11:46:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>条款显示，塔塔之子 (Tata Sons) 寻求从 TCS 股份出售中获得 11 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/tata-sons-seeks-1-1-billion-from-tcs-share-sale-terms-show</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社获得的交易条款显示，塔塔儿子有限公司 (Tata Sons Ltd.) 正在寻求出售这家印度企业集团软件服务部门的股票，筹集至少 11 亿美元的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/tata-sons-seeks-1-1-billion-from-tcs-share-sale-terms-show</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 11:04:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>可可价格从 2024 年初开始翻倍，延续历史性涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/cocoa-prices-double-from-start-of-2024-extending-historic-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[可可期货在不到三个月内翻了一番，其里程碑式的飙升加剧，增加了消费者的成本，并促使巧克力制造商寻找供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-18/cocoa-prices-double-from-start-of-2024-extending-historic-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Mar 2024 09:54:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
